<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00045</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT CREATING THE VISAYAS DEVELOPMENT AUTHORITY, DEFINING ITS POWERS AND FUNCTIONS, PROVIDING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to encourage investors to help those 3rd to 6th class municipalities in Visayas through investment by providing incentives through lowering the corporate income tax for corporations located in a 3rd to 6th class municipality and which are subsequently engaged in agro-industrial, industrial, commercial, tourist, banking, investment, and financial enterprises.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BENITEZ, JOSE FRANCISCO &quot;KIKO&quot; B.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: LOCAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Paduano (000 2019-07-31)</td><td>2. Valmayor (000 2019-07-31)</td><tr><td>3. Tan (S.A.) (000 2020-02-04)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT ENTERPRISES AND PRIVATIZATION ON 2019-07-23</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SECONDARILY REFERRED TO THE COMMITTEE(S) ON VISAYAS DEVELOPMENT</td></tr></table>